HEADWORD: Ripieno
<hw>Ri*pi*e"no</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[It.]</ety>
<fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>Filling up; supplementary; supernumerary; -- a
term applied to those instruments which only swell the mass or
<xex>tutti</xex> of an orchestra, but are not obbligato.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

